* Rename racoon binary to appname.racoon or racoon.appname

* Improve certificate handling

* Allow psk passwords

* Flush setkey SAs for changed peers.

* Disable ipsec tunnel when disabled doh


Policy handling
---------------

Startup: Build all peer configs, Flush all SPDs

Before editing: Delete peer config, Delete SPD for peer

After editing: Build peer config, Add SPD for peer


Don't add if disabled.


DNS
---

Set DNS, refer to http://hi-android.info/src/com/android/server/vpn/VpnService.java.html
